    <item>
      <title>由于手袋需求强劲，爱马仕销量超越古驰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hermes-sales-climb-as-birkin-bag-maker-shows-resilience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于铂金包制造商爱马仕 (Hermes) 的高价手袋需求强劲，其销售额出现上涨，顶住了奢侈品市场整体低迷的冲击，而古驰 (Gucci) 所有者开云集团 (Kering SA) 等同行也未能摆脱这种困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hermes-sales-climb-as-birkin-bag-maker-shows-resilience</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 06:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雷诺新车型需求强劲，助力欧洲汽车市场摆脱低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/renault-confirms-full-year-outlook-on-boost-from-new-models</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷诺汽车公司确认了其全年业绩预期，因为这家法国汽车制造商预计将受益于包括 R5 电动车和升级版 Dacia 运动型多功能车在内的新车型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/renault-confirms-full-year-outlook-on-boost-from-new-models</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
